Superstar Davido is going the extra mile for his much anticipated O2 arena concert by employing the services of legendary American actor and narrator, Morgan Freeman. Freeman noted for his distinctive deep voice, gave the DMW boss’ O2 Arena promotional video a great boost. The popular iconic American media personality with his voice-over for Davido’s London show drove home the singer’s mantra, ‘We rise by lifting others.”   Kunle Afolayan working on another project featuring daughter     Nollywood actor, Kanayo O. Kanayo celebrates 60th birthday     Pretty Mike attends party with ladies dressed as animals   The 29-year-old singer has also made plans for fans who wouldn’t be able to attend by partnering with a digital streaming platform for the global Livestream of his concert at the O2 arena, London on March 5, 2022.c According to the “Champion Sound” singer, “I want my fans worldwide to be a part of this moment as we take Africa to the world.”